Session replay

Reproduce every user session with a pixel-perfect replay

  • See DOM state, network logs, Javascript errors, and performance data for in-depth debugging
  • Search for sessions by user to quickly resolve support tickets and user-reported issues
  • Make better product decisions by watching real users interact with your web or mobile app
Learn more

Session replay

Reproduce every user session with a pixel-perfect replay

  • See DOM state, network logs, Javascript errors, and performance data for in-depth debugging
  • Search for sessions by user to quickly resolve support tickets and user-reported issues
  • Make better product decisions by watching real users interact with your web or mobile app
Learn more

Frontend performance monitoring

Correlate frontend performance with business impact

  • Monitor page load times, CPU / memory usage, browser crashes, and React component rendering
  • See how performance affects conversion rates and engagement
Learn more

Frontend performance monitoring

Correlate frontend performance with business impact

  • Monitor page load times, CPU / memory usage, browser crashes, and React component rendering
  • See how performance affects conversion rates and engagement
Learn more

Product analytics

Convert, engage, and retain customers

  • Create custom metrics to see changes in any interaction, page, or feature
  • Track funnel conversions, user flows, and event volumes
  • Proactively surface issues that prevent product usage and conversion
Learn more

Product analytics

Convert, engage, and retain customers

  • Create custom metrics to see changes in any interaction, page, or feature
  • Track funnel conversions, user flows, and event volumes
  • Proactively surface issues that prevent product usage and conversion

Error tracking and management

Surface the most impactful issues affecting your users

  • Monitor Javascript errors, network failures, and performance issues
  • Review stacktraces alongside video replay of every issue
  • Cut through the noise of error tracking tools to find and categorize your highest-priority issues
Learn more

Error tracking and management

  • Monitor Javascript errors, network failures, and performance issues
  • Review stacktraces alongside video replay of every issue
  • Cut through the noise of error tracking tools to find and categorize your highest-priority issues

User experience analytics

Increase engagement and improve the design of your apps

  • Use heatmaps, clickmaps, and scroll maps to optimize page layouts
  • Surface and quantify how user frustrations like rage clicks and dead clicks hurt product adoption and conversion
Learn more

layoutErrorsList.outerHtml:
Increase NPS, retention, and customer lifetime value

Uncover the exact issue and moment that led to a poor user experience

  • Integrate LogRocket with Qualtrics, Wootric, Delighted, and other experience management tools to see why customers score NPS poorly or leave bad reviews
  • Correlate the effects bugs and slow performance have on feature adoption and NPS
  • Learn how to drive users to the experiences you want them to view

Increase NPS, retention, and customer lifetime value

Uncover the exact issue and moment that led to a poor user experience

  • Integrate LogRocket with Qualtrics, Wootric, Delighted, and other experience management tools to see why customers score NPS poorly or leave bad reviews
  • Correlate the effects bugs and slow performance have on feature adoption and NPS
  • Learn how to drive users to the experiences you want them to view

Increase engagement with important pages or features in your web and mobile apps

Combine quantitative and qualitative user data with technical product information for a comprehensive look into your user experience

  • Know what features turn newly acquired users into regular users
  • Easily build custom funnels and engagement charts based on events like page views, clicks, checkouts, and custom events
  • Uncover technical issues that have a statistically significant impact on engagement metrics

Increase engagement with important pages or features in your web and mobile apps

Combine quantitative and qualitative user data with technical product information for a comprehensive look into your user experience

  • Know what features turn newly acquired users into regular users
  • Easily build custom funnels and engagement charts based on events like page views, clicks, checkouts, and custom events
  • Uncover technical issues that have a statistically significant impact on engagement metrics

Make data-driven design decisions

Understand the user journey and adjust your product to drive usage

  • Optimize layout design by analyzing aggregate user activity on a page
  • See the range of paths users take through your app to understand drop-off or confusing UX
  • Visualize user interactions in aggregate with heatmaps, clickmaps, and scroll maps
  • Drill down to see exactly what a positive interaction looks like

layoutErrorsList.outerHtml:
Stop guessing why bugs happen

  • Understand every bug and user-reported issue with a pixel-perfect video replay
  • See network logs, Javascript errors, and performance telemetry for in-depth debugging
  • Guide your users to a resolution with live co-browse
Learn more

Stop guessing why bugs happen

  • Understand every bug and user-reported issue with a pixel-perfect video replay
  • See network logs, Javascript errors, and performance telemetry for in-depth debugging
  • Guide your users to a resolution with live co-browse
Learn more

Proactively surface issues that impact user conversion rates

  • Surface technical and UX issues that negatively impact conversion
  • Easily build custom funnels based on events like page views, clicks, checkouts, and custom events
  • See how users journey through your checkout flows and what behaviors result in higher conversion rates
Learn more

  • Use heatmaps and scroll maps to make data-driven design decisions

layoutErrorsList.outerHtml:
Understand every bug and customer issue

Replay problems as if they happened in your own browser

  • Watch a video replay of exactly what the user saw
  • See network logs, Javascript errors, and performance telemetry for in-depth debugging
  • Review stacktraces to discover the exact line of broken code

Understand every bug and customer issue

Replay problems as if they happened in your own browser

  • Watch a video replay of exactly what the user saw
  • See network logs, Javascript errors, and performance telemetry for in-depth debugging
  • Review stacktraces to discover the exact line of broken code

Reduce time spent resolving support tickets

LogRocket integrates with your support workflow and displays what went wrong for users so you can help them

  • Follow along with a live video of what the user is seeing and guide them to a solution
  • Integrate LogRocket with Zendesk, Intercom, Salesforce, and other help desks for streamlined support workflows
  • Send sessions directly to JIRA, GitHub, Trello, and other collaboration tools for faster fixes

Reduce time spent resolving support tickets

LogRocket integrates with your support workflow and displays what went wrong for users so you can help them

  • Follow along with a live video of what the user is seeing and guide them to a solution
  • Integrate LogRocket with Zendesk, Intercom, Salesforce, and other help desks for streamlined support workflows
  • Send sessions directly to JIRA, GitHub, Trello, and other collaboration tools for faster fixes

Prevent regressions with intelligent alerting and monitoring

Get notified of issues that impact your users before they report them

  • Easily set up alerts to find out if similar issues recur
  • Surface regressions in new releases of your application
  • Integrate LogRocket with Slack, PagerDuty, or email for contextual alerting

Prevent regressions with intelligent alerting and monitoring

Get notified of issues that impact your users before they report them

  • Easily set up alerts to find out if similar issues recur
  • Surface regressions in new releases of your application
  • Integrate LogRocket with Slack, PagerDuty, or email for contextual alerting

Prioritize issues with the greatest impact on your users

Cut through the noise of error tracking tools — automatically surface and categorize your highest-priority issues

  • See how specific technical issues affect conversion rates, engagement, and NPS
  • Monitor how frequently issues occur and which cohorts they impact
  • Spend your time fixing the most important issues

layoutErrorsList.outerHtml:
Know why users drop off, not just where

Understand and optimize your funnels for increased conversions, trials, activations, and onboarding success

  • See the errors, performance issues, user experiences, rage clicks, and dead clicks that have a statistically significant impact on conversion rates
  • Easily build custom funnels based on events like page views, clicks, checkouts, and custom events

Know why users drop off, not just where

Understand and optimize your funnels for increased conversions, trials, activations, and onboarding success

  • See the errors, performance issues, user experiences, rage clicks, and dead clicks that have a statistically significant impact on conversion rates
  • Easily build custom funnels based on events like page views, clicks, checkouts, and custom events

Understand how users move through your web and mobile apps

Visualize the end user journey to better understand drop-off and where users go after landing in your app

  • Uncover which paths lead to the highest conversion rates
  • Watch session replays to understand what drives users down each path
  • Debug technical and user experience issues that cause users to drop off

Understand how users move through your web and mobile apps

Visualize the end user journey to better understand drop-off and where users go after landing in your app

  • Uncover which paths lead to the highest conversion rates
  • Watch session replays to understand what drives users down each path
  • Debug technical and user experience issues that cause users to drop off

Discover the behaviors that lead to higher conversion rates

To help you drive more revenue, LogRocket identifies user behaviors that are correlated with higher conversion rates

  • See how specific design changes can increase conversion rates
  • Assess how conversion rates have changed over time to quickly catch regressions and ensure continual improvement

  • See how specific design changes can increase conversion rates
